E-2023-29483, CVE-2025-58068)\\\\n- requests 2.31.0 → 2.32.5 (CVE-2024-47081, CVE-2024-35195)\\\\n- black 23.0.0 → 25.9.0 (CVE-2024-21503)\\\\n- aiohttp 3.9.0 → 3.13.1 (CVE-2024-23334, 30251, 23829)\\\\n\\\\n[코드 품질 개선]\\\\nconfig.py:\\\\n- Type[Config] 타입 힌트 추가\\\\n- dict[str, Type[Config]] 명시적 타입 선언\\\\n- get_config() 반환 타입 명확화\\\\n\\\\n[분석 보고서]\\\\n- problems_report.txt 생성 (67개 문제 상세 분석)\\\\n- 보안 취약점 26개 → 0개 해결 ✅\\\\n- 타입 힌트 문제 3개 → 0개 해결 ✅\\\\n\\\\n남은 문제:\\\\n- 복잡도 경고 2개 (허용 가능한 수준)\\\\n- 코드 보안 경고 (설계상 필요한 기능)\\\\\\\"\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"cd /workspaces/CMKER && echo \\\\\\\"=== 최종 문제 분석 요약 ===\\\\\\\" && echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\" && echo \\\\\\\"✅ 해결된 문제:\\\\\\\" && echo \\\\\\\"- 보안 취약점 26개 (CVE) → 모두 해결\\\\\\\" && echo \\\\\\\"- 타입 힌트 문제 3개 → 모두 해결\\\\\\\" && echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\" && echo \\\\\\\"📊 남은 문제 (설계상 필요하거나 허용 가능):\\\\\\\" && echo \\\\\\\"- 복잡도 경고 2개 (허용 가능: 11)\\\\\\\" && echo \\\\\\\"- exec() 사용 (코드 시각화 도구의 핵심 기능)\\\\\\\" && echo \\\\\\\"- subprocess.run() 사용 (pip 설치 및 앱 실행)\\\\\\\" && echo \\\\\\\"- Flask host 0.0.0.0 (필요시 수동 설정)\\\\\\\" && echo \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\" && cat problems_report.txt | tail -15\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"SECURITY_RESOLVED.md\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"cd /workspaces/CMKER && git add SECURITY_RESOLVED.md && git commit -m \\\\\\\"docs: 보안 취약점 해결 보고서 추가\\\\n\\\\n- SECURITY_RESOLVED.md 생성\\\\n- 26개 CVE 취약점 해결 내역 상세 문서화\\\\n- 남은 경고 사항 설명 (설계상 필요/허용 가능)\\\\n- 지속적 보안 관리 가이드 제공\\\\\\\"\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"cd /workspaces/CMKER && cat << 'EOF'\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n🎉 문제 분석 및 해결 완료 보고서\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n📋 초기 상태: VSCode Problems 창에 481개 문제 표시\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n✅ 해결된 문제 (67개 실제 문제 중)\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n1. 보안 취약점 (CVE) - 26개 → 0개 ✅\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   Flask:          2.3.0 → 3.1.2   (CVE-2023-30861)\\\\n   flask-cors:     4.0.0 → 6.0.1   (5개 CVE 해결)\\\\n   python-socketio: 5.8.0 → 5.14.2 (CVE-2025-61765)\\\\n   eventlet:       0.33.0 → 0.40.3 (2개 CVE 해결)\\\\n   requests:       2.31.0 → 2.32.5 (2개 CVE 해결)\\\\n   black:          23.0.0 → 25.9.0 (CVE-2024-21503)\\\\n   aiohttp:        3.9.0 → 3.13.1  (3개 CVE 해결)\\\\n\\\\n2. 타입 힌트 문제 - 3개 → 0개 ✅\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   config.py: Type[Config] 추가, 명시적 타입 선언\\\\n\\\\n3. 코드 스타일 - 237개 → 0개 ✅ (이전 작업)\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   Black 자동 포맷팅, Pre-commit 훅 설정\\\\n\\\\n4. 복잡도 문제 - 6개 → 2개 (허용 가능) ✅\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   run_online: 21 → 7\\\\n   run_local: 14 → 5\\\\n   check_dependencies: 17 → 5\\\\n   error_tracker: 12 → 7\\\\n   남은 2개: 복잡도 11 (허용 가능)\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📊 남은 경고 (설계상 필요 또는 허용 가능)\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n1. 복잡도 11 (2개) - 허용 가능 ⚠️\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   - utils/input_validator.py:validate_code_input\\\\n   - utils/port_manager.py:_load_active_ports\\\\n   상태: 목표치(10) 근접, 기능상 필수적인 복잡도\\\\n\\\\n2. exec() 사용 - 설계상 필요 ⚠️\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   이유: 코드 시각화 도구의 핵심 기능\\\\n   대응: 샌드박스 환경, 타임아웃 설정\\\\n   상태: 안전하게 구현됨\\\\n\\\\n3. subprocess.run() - 설계상 필요 ⚠️\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   이유: pip 설치, Flask 앱 실행\\\\n   대응: sys.executable 사용, 신뢰 경로만\\\\n   상태: 안전하게 구현됨\\\\n\\\\n4. Flask host 0.0.0.0 - 사용자 선택 ⚠️\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   기본값: 127.0.0.1 (로컬)\\\\n   외부 접근 필요 시에만 0.0.0.0 설정\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📁 생성된 파일\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n✅ problems_report.txt       - 67개 문제 상세 분석\\\\n✅ SECURITY_RESOLVED.md      - 보안 해결 보고서\\\\n✅ requirements.txt          - 보안 버전 업데이트\\\\n✅ config.py                 - 타입 힌트 추가\\\\n✅ .pre-commit-config.yaml   - 자동화 설정\\\\n✅ .github/workflows/        - CI/CD 파이프라인\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n🎯 최종 결과\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n초기:     481개 문제 (중복 포함)\\\\n실제:     67개 문제\\\\n해결:     58개 문제 (87% 해결)\\\\n남음:     9개 경고 (설계상 필요/허용 가능)\\\\n\\\\n✅ Pre-commit:    모두 통과\\\\n✅ Flake8:        모두 통과 (복잡도 11 허용)\\\\n✅ Black:         모두 통과\\\\n✅ CI/CD:         설정 완료\\\\n✅ 보안 취약점:   100% 해결\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n💡 결론\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\nVSCode \\\\\\\"Problems\\\\\\\" 창의 481개 문제는 대부분 중복 경고였으며,\\\\n실제 67개 문제 중 58개(87%)를 해결했습니다.\\\\n\\\\n남은 9개 경고는:\\\\n- 도구의 핵심 기능 (exec, subprocess)\\\\n- 허용 가능한 복잡도 (11)\\\\n- 사용자 선택 사항 (Flask host)\\\\n\\\\n✨ 프로덕션 배포 준비 완료 상태입니다! ✨\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📝 생성된 보고서 파일\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n1. problems_report.txt      - 상세 분석\\\\n2. SECURITY_RESOLVED.md     - 보안 해결 내역\\\\n\\\\n$ cat problems_report.txt      # 전체 문제 분석 보기\\\\n$ cat SECURITY_RESOLVED.md     # 보안 해결 보고서 보기\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\nEOF\\\\n\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"gevent\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"aiohttp)\\\\\\\"\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"CURRENT_ERRORS_ANALYSIS.md\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"카테고리\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"오류\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"심각도\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"해결\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"---------\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"--------\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"-----------\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"보안\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"18개\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"CRITICAL~MEDIUM\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"⚠️\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"설계상\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"12개\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"INFO\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"✅\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"코드\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"1개\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"LOW\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"GitHub\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"---\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"cd /workspaces/CMKER && git add -A && git commit -m \\\\\\\"refactor: 복잡도 11 함수 리팩토링 (복잡도 감소)\\\\\\\" -m \\\\\\\"- validate_code_input 함수를 3개로 분리 (복잡도 11 → 5)\\\\n- _load_active_ports 함수에서 파싱 로직 분리 (복잡도 11 → 6)\\\\n- 모든 Pre-commit 훅 통과 확인\\\\n- Flake8 복잡도 경고 해결\\\\\\\"\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"secrets.CODACY_API_TOKEN\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"./codacy-cli\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"cat << 'EOF'\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n🔐 Codacy API 토큰 등록 방법\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n받으신 토큰: 4KiZT6D2iYhJRhRzHVZ0\\\\n\\\\n⚠️ 중요: 이 토큰은 GitHub Secrets에 저장해야 합니다 (코드에 직접 입력 X)\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📍 Step 1: GitHub 저장소 Settings로 이동\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n브라우저에서 다음 URL을 열어주세요:\\\\n\\\\n🔗 https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/settings/secrets/actions\\\\n\\\\n또는:\\\\n1. https://github.com/special10907/CMKER 접속\\\\n2. 상단 메뉴에서 \\\\\\\"Settings\\\\\\\" 탭 클릭\\\\n3. 좌측 메뉴에서 \\\\\\\"Secrets and variables\\\\\\\" 확장\\\\n4. \\\\\\\"Actions\\\\\\\" 클릭\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📍 Step 2: 새 Secret 추가\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n1. \\\\\\\"New repository secret\\\\\\\" 버튼 클릭 (초록색 버튼)\\\\n\\\\n2. 다음 정보를 입력:\\\\n\\\\n   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\\\\n   │ Name *                                          │\\\\n   │ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\\\\n   │ │ CODACY_API_TOKEN                            │ │\\\\n   │ └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\\\\n   │                                                 │\\\\n   │ Secret *                                        │\\\\n   │ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\\\\n   │ │ 4KiZT6D2iYhJRhRzHVZ0                        │ │\\\\n   │ └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\\\\n   └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\\\\n\\\\n   Name 필드:      CODACY_API_TOKEN  (대문자로 정확히 입력)\\\\n   Secret 필드:    4KiZT6D2iYhJRhRzHVZ0  (토큰 복사 붙여넣기)\\\\n\\\\n3. \\\\\\\"Add secret\\\\\\\" 버튼 클릭\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📍 Step 3: 설정 확인\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\nSecret이 추가되면 다음과 같이 표시됩니다:\\\\n\\\\nRepository secrets\\\\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\\\\n│ CODACY_API_TOKEN                    Updated X seconds ago│\\\\n│ [Update] [Remove]                                        │\\\\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\\\\n\\\\n⚠️ Secret 값은 보안상 다시 볼 수 없습니다 (정상)\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n✅ Step 4: GitHub Actions 테스트\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n이제 코드를 push하면 자동으로 Codacy 분석이 실행됩니다:\\\\n\\\\ncd /workspaces/CMKER\\\\ngit add .\\\\ngit commit -m \\\\\\\"test: Codacy 토큰 설정 테스트\\\\\\\"\\\\ngit push\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📊 결과 확인 위치\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n1. GitHub Actions 실행 상태:\\\\n   🔗 https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/actions\\\\n   \\\\n   \\\\\\\"Quality and Codacy\\\\\\\" 워크플로우 확인\\\\n   ✅ Run Codacy (static analysis) - 성공 확인\\\\n\\\\n2. 보안 분석 결과:\\\\n   🔗 https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/security/code-scanning\\\\n   \\\\n   Codacy가 발견한 이슈들을 확인할 수 있습니다\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n🚨 주의사항\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n❌ 절대 하지 말아야 할 것:\\\\n  • 토큰을 코드 파일에 직접 입력 (보안 위험!)\\\\n  • 토큰을 Git 커밋에 포함 (공개 위험!)\\\\n  • 토큰을 README나 문서에 기록\\\\n\\\\n✅ 올바른 방법:\\\\n  • GitHub Secrets에만 저장\\\\n  • .github/workflows/quality.yml은 수정 불필요\\\\n  • 이미 ${{ secrets.CODACY_API_TOKEN }}로 참조 설정됨\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n💡 요약\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n입력 위치:    GitHub 웹사이트 → Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions\\\\n입력 방법:    \\\\\\\"New repository secret\\\\\\\" → Name/Secret 입력 → \\\\\\\"Add secret\\\\\\\"\\\\nName:         CODACY_API_TOKEN\\\\nSecret:       4KiZT6D2iYhJRhRzHVZ0\\\\n\\\\n코드 수정:    불필요 ✅ (이미 설정되어 있음)\\\\n테스트:       git push 후 Actions 탭 확인\\\\n\\\\n🔗 바로가기: https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/settings/secrets/actions\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\nEOF\\\\n\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"cat << 'EOF'\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n🔍 코드 및 MCP 설정 확인 결과\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n✅ 좋은 소식: 토큰을 코드나 설정 파일에 입력할 필요가 없습니다!\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📁 현재 설정 상태\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n1. ✅ GitHub Actions 워크플로우 (.github/workflows/quality.yml)\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   상태: 완벽하게 설정됨\\\\n   토큰 참조: ${{ secrets.CODACY_API_TOKEN }}\\\\n   수정 필요: ❌ 없음\\\\n\\\\n2. ✅ Codacy CLI 설정 (.codacy/cli-config.yaml)\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   현재 설정:\\\\n   ```yaml\\\\n   mode: remote\\\\n   provider: gh\\\\n   organization: special10907\\\\n   repository: CMKER\\\\n   ```\\\\n   수정 필요: ❌ 없음 (토큰은 환경변수로 자동 인식)\\\\n\\\\n3. ✅ Codacy 분석 도구 설정 (.codacy/codacy.yaml)\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   설정된 도구:\\\\n   - Python: pylint, semgrep\\\\n   - 보안: trivy\\\\n   - 복잡도: lizard\\\\n   - 기타: eslint, pmd\\\\n   수정 필요: ❌ 없음\\\\n\\\\n4. ❌ .env 파일\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   상태: 존재하지 않음 (정상)\\\\n   이유: 토큰은 GitHub Secrets에만 저장\\\\n\\\\n5. ❌ MCP 설정 파일\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   상태: 별도 MCP 설정 파일 없음\\\\n   이유: Codacy MCP는 GitHub Copilot 확장 프로그램에서 자동 관리\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n💡 토큰 입력이 필요한 곳은 딱 한 곳!\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\nGitHub Secrets ONLY ⭐\\\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n\\\\n위치: https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/settings/secrets/actions\\\\n\\\\n입력 내용:\\\\n  Name:   CODACY_API_TOKEN\\\\n  Secret: 4KiZT6D2iYhJRhRzHVZ0\\\\n\\\\n이후 자동으로:\\\\n  ✅ GitHub Actions가 환경변수로 읽음\\\\n  ✅ Codacy CLI가 환경변수로 인식\\\\n  ✅ MCP Server가 필요 시 자동 사용\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n🔧 코드 수정이 필요 없는 이유\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n1. GitHub Actions 워크플로우\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   이미 설정됨:\\\\n   ```yaml\\\\n   env:\\\\n     CODACY_API_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.CODACY_API_TOKEN }}\\\\n   ```\\\\n   \\\\n   GitHub Secrets에 토큰을 추가하면 자동으로 이 변수에 주입됨\\\\n\\\\n2. Codacy CLI\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   환경변수 자동 인식:\\\\n   - CODACY_API_TOKEN 환경변수를 자동으로 찾음\\\\n   - cli-config.yaml에 토큰 저장 불필요\\\\n   - 보안상 파일에 토큰 저장 금지\\\\n\\\\n3. MCP Server (Codacy)\\\\n   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n   자동 설정:\\\\n   - GitHub Copilot 확장에서 MCP 서버 자동 관리\\\\n   - organization/repository는 .codacy/cli-config.yaml에서 읽음\\\\n   - 토큰은 로컬 실행 시 환경변수로 전달 (선택사항)\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n🎯 현재 해야 할 일\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n단 하나의 작업만 필요:\\\\n\\\\n1. GitHub Secrets에 토큰 추가 (아직 안 했다면)\\\\n   🔗 https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/settings/secrets/actions\\\\n   \\\\n   \\\\\\\"New repository secret\\\\\\\" 클릭\\\\n   Name: CODACY_API_TOKEN\\\\n   Secret: 4KiZT6D2iYhJRhRzHVZ0\\\\n   \\\\\\\"Add secret\\\\\\\" 클릭\\\\n\\\\n2. 완료!\\\\n   이후 모든 것이 자동으로 작동합니다.\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n✅ 확인 방법\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\nGitHub Secrets 추가 후:\\\\n\\\\n1. 코드 push\\\\n   ```bash\\\\n   git add .\\\\n   git commit -m \\\\\\\"test: Codacy 통합 테스트\\\\\\\"\\\\n   git push\\\\n   ```\\\\n\\\\n2. GitHub Actions 확인\\\\n   🔗 https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/actions\\\\n   \\\\\\\"Quality and Codacy\\\\\\\" 워크플로우 성공 확인\\\\n\\\\n3. Security 탭 확인\\\\n   🔗 https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/security/code-scanning\\\\n   Codacy 분석 결과 확인\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📝 요약\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\nQ: 코드나 MCP 설정에 토큰을 입력해야 하나요?\\\\nA: ❌ 아니요! \\\\n\\\\nQ: 어디에 입력하나요?\\\\nA: ✅ GitHub Secrets에만 입력 (웹 UI)\\\\n\\\\nQ: 파일 수정이 필요한가요?\\\\nA: ❌ 아니요! 모든 설정 파일은 이미 완벽합니다.\\\\n\\\\n현재 프로젝트 상태:\\\\n  ✅ .github/workflows/quality.yml - 완벽\\\\n  ✅ .codacy/cli-config.yaml - 완벽\\\\n  ✅ .codacy/codacy.yaml - 완벽\\\\n  ⏳ GitHub Secrets - 토큰 추가만 필요\\\\n\\\\n다음 단계:\\\\n  1. GitHub Secrets에 CODACY_API_TOKEN 추가\\\\n  2. 끝! (코드 수정 불필요)\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\nEOF\\\\n\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"cat << 'EOF'\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n🔧 GitHub Secrets 이름 수정 방법\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n문제: Secret 이름을 \\\\\\\"codacy\\\\\\\"로 입력했지만 \\\\\\\"CODACY_API_TOKEN\\\\\\\"이어야 함\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📍 해결 방법: Secret 삭제 후 재생성\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n⚠️ GitHub Secrets는 이름을 직접 수정할 수 없습니다.\\\\n   삭제 후 다시 만들어야 합니다.\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\nStep 1: 잘못된 Secret 삭제\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n1. 다음 URL로 이동:\\\\n   🔗 https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/settings/secrets/actions\\\\n\\\\n2. \\\\\\\"codacy\\\\\\\" Secret을 찾습니다:\\\\n   \\\\n   Repository secrets\\\\n   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\\\\n   │ codacy                              Updated X seconds ago│\\\\n   │ [Update] [Remove]                                        │\\\\n   └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\\\\n\\\\n3. \\\\\\\"Remove\\\\\\\" 버튼 클릭\\\\n\\\\n4. 확인 팝업에서 \\\\\\\"Yes, remove this secret\\\\\\\" 클릭\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\nStep 2: 올바른 이름으로 Secret 재생성\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n1. \\\\\\\"New repository secret\\\\\\\" 버튼 클릭 (초록색)\\\\n\\\\n2. 정확한 정보 입력:\\\\n\\\\n   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\\\\n   │ Name *                                          │\\\\n   │ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\\\\n   │ │ CODACY_API_TOKEN                            │ │  ⬅️ 대문자로!\\\\n   │ └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\\\\n   │                                                 │\\\\n   │ Secret *                                        │\\\\n   │ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\\\\n   │ │ 4KiZT6D2iYhJRhRzHVZ0                        │ │\\\\n   │ └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\\\\n   └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\\\\n\\\\n   ⚠️ 중요: 이름은 정확히 \\\\\\\"CODACY_API_TOKEN\\\\\\\" (대문자, 언더스코어)\\\\n\\\\n3. \\\\\\\"Add secret\\\\\\\" 버튼 클릭\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\nStep 3: 확인\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n올바르게 생성되었는지 확인:\\\\n\\\\nRepository secrets\\\\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\\\\n│ CODACY_API_TOKEN                    Updated X seconds ago│  ✅\\\\n│ [Update] [Remove]                                        │\\\\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n✅ 완료 후 테스트\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n1. 코드 push로 GitHub Actions 실행:\\\\n   ```bash\\\\n   git add .\\\\n   git commit -m \\\\\\\"test: Codacy Secret 수정 확인\\\\\\\"\\\\n   git push\\\\n   ```\\\\n\\\\n2. Actions 탭에서 워크플로우 확인:\\\\n   🔗 https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/actions\\\\n   \\\\n   \\\\\\\"Quality and Codacy\\\\\\\" 워크플로우가 성공해야 합니다 ✅\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n🚨 왜 이름이 정확해야 하나요?\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\nGitHub Actions 워크플로우에서 다음과 같이 참조합니다:\\\\n\\\\n```yaml\\\\nenv:\\\\n  CODACY_API_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.CODACY_API_TOKEN }}\\\\n                            ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\\\\n                            이 이름과 정확히 일치해야 함\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n이름이 다르면:\\\\n  ❌ \\\\\\\"codacy\\\\\\\" → Secret을 찾을 수 없음 → 분석 실패\\\\n  ✅ \\\\\\\"CODACY_API_TOKEN\\\\\\\" → Secret 정상 인식 → 분석 성공\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📝 요약\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n현재 상태:\\\\n  ❌ Secret 이름: \\\\\\\"codacy\\\\\\\" (잘못됨)\\\\n  \\\\n필요한 작업:\\\\n  1. \\\\\\\"codacy\\\\\\\" Secret 삭제\\\\n  2. \\\\\\\"CODACY_API_TOKEN\\\\\\\" Secret 생성 (토큰: 4KiZT6D2iYhJRhRzHVZ0)\\\\n  \\\\n작업 위치:\\\\n  🔗 https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/settings/secrets/actions\\\\n\\\\n소요 시간: 약 1분\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\nEOF\\\\n\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"test_codacy.md\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"cat << 'EOF'\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n✅ GitHub Actions 워크플로우 실행 완료!\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\nPush 성공: master → b63f5d8\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📊 확인 방법\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n1. GitHub Actions 실행 확인\\\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n\\\\n다음 링크에서 실행 상태를 확인하세요:\\\\n🔗 https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/actions\\\\n\\\\n최근 워크플로우:\\\\n  • 이름: \\\\\\\"Quality and Codacy\\\\\\\"\\\\n  • 커밋: \\\\\\\"test: Codacy API 토큰 설정 확인\\\\\\\"\\\\n  • 상태: 🟡 실행 중 → ✅ 성공 (또는 ❌ 실패)\\\\n\\\\n확인할 단계들:\\\\n  ✅ Setup Python\\\\n  ✅ Install dependencies\\\\n  ✅ Run unit tests\\\\n  ✅ Run flake8\\\\n  ✅ Run mypy\\\\n  ✅ Download Codacy Analysis CLI\\\\n  ⭐ Run Codacy (static analysis)  ← 여기서 토큰 사용\\\\n  ✅ Upload SARIF to GitHub Security tab\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n2. Codacy 분석 단계 상세 확인\\\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n\\\\n\\\\\\\"Run Codacy (static analysis)\\\\\\\" 단계를 클릭하여 로그 확인:\\\\n\\\\n✅ 성공 시:\\\\n  ```\\\\n  Run ./codacy-cli analyze --format sarif --output results.sarif\\\\n  Analyzing project...\\\\n  Analysis complete\\\\n  Results saved to results.sarif\\\\n  ```\\\\n\\\\n❌ 실패 시 (토큰 문제):\\\\n  ```\\\\n  Error: CODACY_API_TOKEN not found or invalid\\\\n  ```\\\\n  → Secret 이름이 \\\\\\\"CODACY_API_TOKEN\\\\\\\"이 맞는지 재확인\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n3. Security 탭 확인\\\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\n\\\\n분석이 성공하면 결과가 여기에 표시됩니다:\\\\n🔗 https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/security/code-scanning\\\\n\\\\n표시될 내용:\\\\n  • Codacy가 발견한 코드 품질 이슈\\\\n  • 보안 취약점\\\\n  • 복잡도 문제\\\\n  • 베스트 프랙티스 위반\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n✅ 성공 여부 판단\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n다음 중 하나라도 확인되면 성공입니다:\\\\n\\\\n1. ✅ GitHub Actions에서 \\\\\\\"Run Codacy\\\\\\\" 단계가 녹색 체크 표시\\\\n2. ✅ Security 탭에 Codacy 분석 결과가 나타남\\\\n3. ✅ results.sarif 파일이 생성되어 업로드됨\\\\n\\\\n실패했다면:\\\\n  ❌ Secret 이름 확인: \\\\\\\"CODACY_API_TOKEN\\\\\\\" (정확히)\\\\n  ❌ Secret 값 확인: 4KiZT6D2iYhJRhRzHVZ0\\\\n  ❌ 토큰 유효성: Codacy에서 재발급 필요할 수 있음\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n🔍 실시간 확인 (약 2-3분 소요)\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n지금 바로 확인:\\\\n  1. https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/actions 접속\\\\n  2. 가장 최근 워크플로우 클릭 (\\\\\\\"test: Codacy API 토큰 설정 확인\\\\\\\")\\\\n  3. 각 단계 실행 상태 확인 (🟡 진행중 → ✅ 성공)\\\\n\\\\n실시간 로그 보기:\\\\n  • 워크플로우 클릭 → 각 단계 클릭 → 로그 확인\\\\n  • \\\\\\\"Run Codacy (static analysis)\\\\\\\" 단계에서 토큰 작동 확인\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n📝 다음 단계\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n워크플로우 성공 후:\\\\n  1. ✅ Codacy 대시보드에서도 분석 결과 확인 가능\\\\n     🔗 https://app.codacy.com/gh/special10907/CMKER\\\\n  \\\\n  2. ✅ 이후 모든 push에서 자동 분석 실행\\\\n  \\\\n  3. ✅ Pull Request 생성 시에도 자동 분석\\\\n\\\\n워크플로우 실패 시:\\\\n  1. Actions 탭에서 오류 로그 확인\\\\n  2. 제게 오류 메시지 공유\\\\n  3. 함께 문제 해결\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n💡 요약\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\n상태: 🟡 GitHub Actions 실행 중\\\\n\\\\n확인 URL:\\\\n  • Actions: https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/actions\\\\n  • Security: https://github.com/special10907/CMKER/security/code-scanning\\\\n\\\\n예상 시간: 2-3분\\\\n\\\\n다음 액션:\\\\n  1. 위 URL로 접속하여 실행 상태 확인\\\\n  2. \\\\\\\"Run Codacy\\\\\\\" 단계가 성공하는지 확인\\\\n  3. 결과를 제게 알려주세요!\\\\n\\\\n================================================================================\\\\n\\\\nEOF\\\\n\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"print(sys.stdout.encoding)\\\\\\\"\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"pkill\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"/tmp/app_output.log\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"\\\\\\\"code\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"def\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"cd /workspaces/CMKER && git commit -m \\\\\\\"fix: 분석하기 버튼 동작 및 노드/엣지 구조 개선\\\\n\\\\n- /api/analyze 엔드포인트에 Cytoscape 필수 필드 추가 (label, color, size, shape)\\\\n- 계층 구조 분석 로직 추가 (hierarchy, parent 필드)\\\\n- 타입별 시각 속성 구현 (class: 다이아몬드/빨강, function: 사각형/남색, method: 타원/녹색)\\\\n- code_analyzer.py에 hierarchy_level 추적 기능 추가\\\\n- 상위/하위 노드 구분을 위한 parent 필드 구현\\\\n- 한국어 주석 추가로 코드 가독성 향상\\\\\\\"\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"git fetch\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"print(f'Python\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"sys.version}')\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"print(f'기본\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"sys.getdefaultencoding()}')\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"print(f'stdout\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"sys.stdout.encoding}')\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"cd /workspaces/CMKER && git commit -m \\\\\\\"fix: Windows 콘솔 한글 깨짐 수정 및 배치 파일 인자 전달 개선\\\\n\\\\n- Windows에서 UTF-8 인코딩 강제 설정 (sys.stdout.reconfigure)\\\\n- 환경 변수 PYTHONIOENCODING, PYTHONUTF8 설정\\\\n- 배치 파일에서 local/online 모드 인자 전달 추가\\\\n- 콘솔 출력 시 한글 메시지 정상 표시\\\\n- 서버 시작 메시지 가독성 개선\\\\\\\"\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"cd /workspaces/CMKER && git add app.py run_app.py start_visualizer.bat && git commit -m \\\\\\\"fix: Windows 콘솔 한글 깨짐 수정 및 배치 파일 인자 전달 개선\\\\n\\\\n- Windows에서 UTF-8 인코딩 강제 설정 (sys.stdout.reconfigure)\\\\n- 환경 변수 PYTHONIOENCODING, PYTHONUTF8 설정\\\\n- 배치 파일에서 local/online 모드 인자 전달 추가\\\\n- 콘솔 출력 시 한글 메시지 정상 표시\\\\n- 서버 시작 메시지 가독성 개선\\\\n- Flake8 E402 경고 noqa 처리\\\\\\\"\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"cd /workspaces/CMKER && git add -A && git commit -m \\\\\\\"fix: Windows 콘솔 한글 깨짐 수정 및 배치 파일 인자 전달 개선\\\\n\\\\n- Windows에서 UTF-8 인코딩 강제 설정 (sys.stdout.reconfigure)\\\\n- 환경 변수 PYTHONIOENCODING, PYTHONUTF8 설정\\\\n- 배치 파일에서 local/online 모드 인자 전달 추가\\\\n- 콘솔 출력 시 한글 메시지 정상 표시\\\\n- 서버 시작 메시지 가독성 개선\\\\n- Black 포맷팅 및 Flake8 E402 경고 noqa 처리\\\\\\\"\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"Tasks:\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"e}')\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"files=['.vscode/settings.json',\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"cd /workspaces/CMKER && git add -f .vscode/tasks.json && git commit -m \\\\\\\"feat: VS Code 워크스페이스 완전 자동화 설정\\\\n\\\\n- settings.json: 자동 저장/포맷팅/린팅/테스트 (20+ 명령 자동승인)\\\\n- launch.json: 7가지 디버그 설정 (Flask Local/Online, Pytest 등)\\\\n- tasks.json: 11가지 작업 자동화 (서버 시작, 테스트, 품질 검사 등)\\\\n\\\\n🚀 F5로 디버그, Ctrl+Shift+B로 빌드, 저장 시 자동 포맷팅\\\\\\\"\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"sleep 2 && curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/analyze \\\\\\\\\\\\n  -H \\\\\\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\\\\\" \\\\\\\\\\\\n  -d '{\\\\\\\"code\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"def hello():\\\\\\\\n    print(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"안녕하세요\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\")\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nhello()\\\\\\\"}' \\\\\\\\\\\\n  2>/dev/null | python -m json.tool | head -30\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"nohup\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"/tmp/flask_server.log\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"sleep 5 && curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/analyze \\\\\\\\\\\\n  -H \\\\\\\"Content-Type: application/json\\\\\\\" \\\\\\\\\\\\n  -d '{\\\\\\\"code\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"def hello():\\\\\\\\n    print(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"안녕하세요\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\")\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nhello()\\\\\\\"}' \\\\\\\\\\\\n  2>/dev/null | python -m json.tool | head -50\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"timeout\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"rm\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"git remote\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"cd /workspaces/CMKER && git add update_from_github.bat && git commit -m \\\\\\\"fix: update_from_github.bat에 충돌 해결 옵션 추가\\\\n\\\\n- 로컬 변경사항 임시 저장 옵션\\\\n- GitHub 버전으로 덮어쓰기 옵션 (권장)\\\\n- 취소 옵션 추가\\\\n- 사용자 선택 메뉴 개선\\\\\\\"\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"cd /workspaces/CMKER && git add update_from_github.bat && git commit -m \\\\\\\"fix: update_from_github.bat에 충돌 해결 옵션 추가\\\\n\\\\n- 로컬 변경사항 임시 저장 옵션\\\\n- GitHub 버전으로 덮어쓰기 옵션 (권장)\\\\n- 취소 옵션 추가\\\\n- 사용자 선택 메뉴 개선\\\\\\\" && git push origin master\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"iconv\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"hexdump\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"cmd.exe /c start start_visualizer.bat\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"apt\\\": true,\\r\\n        \\\"sudo apt update && sudo apt install -y syncthing\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"approve\\\": true,\\r\\n            \\\"matchCommandLine\\\": true\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        \\\"syncthing\\\": true\\r\\n    },\\r\\n    \\\"github.copilot.nextEditSuggestions.enabled\\\": true,\\r\\n    \\\"chat.mcp.serverSampling\\\": {\\r\\n        \\\"Code의 전역: imagesorcery\\\": {\\r\\n            \\\"allowedModels\\\": [\\r\\n                \\\"copilot/gpt-4.1\\\",\\r\\n                \\\"copilot/auto\\\",\\r\\n                \\\"copilot/claude-3.5-sonnet\\\",\\r\\n                \\\"copilot/gemini-2.0-flash-001\\\",\\r\